description: Izamar and Krissy take on Dylan and Wenona in round 2. The score is close and the girls are all hungry for a win. We already know Izamar and Krissy are animals on the mat, but they are given a run for her money by team purple. These bitches mean business! It is to close to call which team will end up on top in round 4... but whoever it is, there will be hell to pay!
title: ROUND 2 of July's Tag Team Match! Wild kinky bitches fight it out
